{"word":"H5670 - עָבַט - ʻâbaṭ - aw-bat' - Borrow","slug":"H5670","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָבַט</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâbaṭ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-bat'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Borrow"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D1;&#x05D8; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;bat&#x0323;</b> - <i>aw-bat'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>pawn</i>; causatively to <i>lend</i> (on security); figuratively to <i>entangle: - </i>borrow, break [ranks], fetch [a pledge], lend, X surely."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5667\">H5667</a>, <a href=\"#/H5671\">H5671</a>"}]}